entry.title: Sunfeast Nice 150g
entry.summary:
Vendor: SUNFEAST
Type: Foods
Price: 20.00

Sunfeast Nice biscuits are a classic tea-time snack that are loved by one and all. They are crunchy sugar sprinkled coconut biscuits and have an enticing aroma of vanilla. Each bite of Sunfeast Nice biscuits gives you a delightfully well-balanced sweetness accompanied by the lingering taste of coconuts and vanilla. These crunchy Sunfeast Nice biscuits will surely transform tea-time into your most favourite time of the day!

Key Information:

  • Main Ingredients: Sunfeast Nice biscuits are baked to a crisp golden crust, and with a sprinkle of sugar crystals on top. They also contain coconuts, milk and vanilla flavour among other ingredients.
  • Suitable For: The tempting flavours of coconut and vanilla, and the delicate sweetness of Sunfeast Nice biscuits are an exciting combination. They are not only suitable for tea-time but can also be the snack companion you can count on whenever you desire.
  • Usage: Sunfeast Nice biscuits are an excellent pairing with a hot beverage during tea-time. You can also pair these sweet, and tasty biscuits with a coffee, or a cold glass of milk.
  • Quantity: This pack of Sunfeast Nice biscuits weighs 150g. This quantity is sufficient to be shared with your loved ones and have a good time.

Sunfeast Nice biscuits have a soft coconut flavour, sprinkled sugar crystals and a crisp, golden baked texture. These qualities are inspired by the classic and well-renowned Nice biscuits, named after the French city of the same name. Nice biscuits are a beloved tea-time accompaniment throughout the world. Sunfeast Nice biscuits are prepared with great care to have the most delicate balance sweetness that lingers on after each bite. The dual combination of coconut and vanilla flavours, and the crunch on each bite make for a truly Nice experience.
